'''吉莉安·薛伯·弗琳'''（{{lang|en|'''Gillian Schieber Flynn'''}}，{{bd|1971年|2月24日}}）是一位美国女性作家、编剧和漫画书作者，曾是一位效力于《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》的电视评论家<ref>{{cite web |title=Author Gillian Flynn finds 'Dark Places' in KC |url=http://www.kansascity.com/entertainment/books/story/1223650.html |accessdate=June 1, 2009}}{{Dead link|date=October 2010|bot=H3llBot}}</ref>。目前她已经出版了三部惊悚小说，包括''Sharp Objects'', ''Dark Places'' 和《[[消失的爱人_(小说)|消失的爱人]]》（ ''Gone Girl''）。其中《消失的爱人》于2014年被[[大卫·芬奇|大卫·芬奇]]拍摄成[[消失的愛人_(2014年電影)|同名电影]]，并由她本人担任编剧;而''Dark Places''則於2015年由法國導演吉爾斯·帕奎-布萊納編劇並執導為《[[暗處|暗處]]》。

==生平==
她生于密苏里州[[堪萨斯城|堪萨斯城]]<ref>{{cite news |last=McClurg |first=Jocelyn |title=New voices: Gillian Flynn makes thriller debut |newspaper=USA Today |date=September 27, 2006 |url=http://www.usatoday.com/life/books/news/2006-09-27-new-voices-flynn_x.htm |accessdate=2014-12-15 |archive-date=2012-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120620235209/http://www.usatoday.com/life/books/news/2006-09-27-new-voices-flynn_x.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="kansascity2012">{{cite web |url=http://www.kansascity.com/living/star-magazine/article2485406.html |title=Kansas City native Gillian Flynn emerges as a literary force with her twisted mystery 'Gone Girl' |publisher=''The Kansas City Star'' |date=November 11, 2012 |first=Steve |last=Paul |accessdate=October 11, 2014 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141004025841/http://www.kansascity.com/living/star-magazine/article2485406.html |archivedate=2014年10月4日 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，父母都是 Metropolitan Community College 的教授，母亲 Judith Ann 教授阅读理解，父亲 Edwin Matthew Flynn 教授电影课程<ref name="kansascity2012"/><ref name="timeout2013">{{cite web |url=http://www.timeout.com/chicago/books/gillian-flynn-on-gone-girl-interview |title=Gillian Flynn on Gone Girl - Interview |publisher=TimeOut |date=February 7, 2013 |first=Novid |last=Parsi |accessdate=October 11, 2014 |archive-date=2020-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201006014258/https://www.timeout.com/chicago/books/gillian-flynn-on-gone-girl-interview |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="elle2014">{{cite web |url=http://www.elle.com/pop-culture/reviews/inside-gone-girls-gillian-flynn |title=INSIDE THE DANGEROUS MIND OF GONE GIRL’S GILLIAN FLYNN |publisher=''Elle'' |date=October 10, 2014 |first=Lili |last=Anolik |accessdate=October 11, 2014 |archive-date=2015-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150103232701/http://www.elle.com/pop-culture/reviews/inside-gone-girls-gillian-flynn |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://familytreemaker.genealogy.com/users/c/r/o/Katherine-J-Crofford-CO/WEBSITE-0001/UHP-0495.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-11-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141128023502/http://familytreemaker.genealogy.com/users/c/r/o/Katherine-J-Crofford-CO/WEBSITE-0001/UHP-0495.html |archivedate=2014-11-28 }}</ref>。她有一个哥哥Travis是位铁路机械工程师<ref name="kansascity2012"/>。受家庭的影响，她从小就喜欢阅读、写作和看电影<ref name="kansascity2012"/><ref name="timeout2013"/>。

弗琳毕业于[[堪萨斯大学|堪萨斯大学]]的[[英语|英语]]和[[新闻|新闻]]专业。曾短暂效力于《[[美国新闻与世界报道|美国新闻与世界报道]]》。1998年至2008年为《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》写电视评论和影评<ref name="kansascity2012"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.suntimes.com/entertainment/books/13763359-421/gone-girl-puts-chicago-author-gillian-flynn-in-the-thriller-elite.html#.VDnNA_ldUrU |title=‘Gone Girl’ puts Chicago author Gillian Flynn in the thriller elite |publisher=''Chicago Sun-Times'' |date=July 16, 2012 |first=Mike |last=Thomas |accessdate=October 11, 2014 |archive-date=2014-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141016183011/http://www.suntimes.com/entertainment/books/13763359-421/gone-girl-puts-chicago-author-gillian-flynn-in-the-thriller-elite.html#.VDnNA_ldUrU |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2012-07-28/features/ct-prj-0610-gillian-flynn-20120728_1_poster-child-dark-places-amy |title=Peeking in Gillian Flynn's vault of horror |publisher= |date=July 28, 2012 |first=Kevin |last=Nance |accessdate=October 11, 2014 |archive-date=2014-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141007160143/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2012-07-28/features/ct-prj-0610-gillian-flynn-20120728_1_poster-child-dark-places-amy |dead-url=no }}</ref>，之后担任专职作家。

==个人生活==
2007年她与律师 Brett Nolan 结婚<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.recapo.com/cbs-sunday-morning/cbs-sunday-morning-entertainment/sunday-morning-gillian-flynn-female-characters-gone-girl-movie/ |title=Sunday Morning: Gillian Flynn Female Characters & Gone Girl Movie |publisher=ReCapo |accessdate=October 12, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022143803/http://www.recapo.com/cbs-sunday-morning/cbs-sunday-morning-entertainment/sunday-morning-gillian-flynn-female-characters-gone-girl-movie/ |archive-date=2014-10-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，两人育有2个孩子<ref name="elle2014"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.people.com/article/gillian-flynn-gone-girl-five-things |title=5 Things to Know About Gone Girl Author Gillian Flynn |publisher=''People'' |date=October 3, 2014 |first=Michelle |last=Tauber |accessdate=October 11, 2014 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308000328/http://www.people.com/article/gillian-flynn-gone-girl-five-things |dead-url=no }}</ref>。自从30多岁时她就与家人一起居住在[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]<ref name=TG>{{cite news |title=Gillian Flynn on her bestseller Gone Girl and accusations of misogyny |url=http://www.theguardian.com/books/2013/may/01/gillian-flynn-bestseller-gone-girl-misogyny |newspaper=The Guardian |first=Oliver |last=Burkeman |date=May 1, 2013 |accessdate=2014-12-15 |archive-date=2017-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170214202253/https://www.theguardian.com/books/2013/may/01/gillian-flynn-bestseller-gone-girl-misogyny |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

